Package eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board

Class Item

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, SearchTreeObject, Drawable, ShapeTree.Storable, UndoableObjects.Storable, Serializable, Comparable<Object>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BoardOutline, ComponentOutline, DrillItem, ObstacleArea, Trace
public abstract class Item extends Object implements Drawable, SearchTreeObject, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, UndoableObjects.Storable, Serializable
Basic class of the items on a board.

      Returns the set of all Connectable items of the net with number p_net_no which can be reached recursively via normal contacts from this item. If p_net_no <= 0, the net number is ignored. If p_stop_at_plane, the recursive algorithm stops, when a conduction area is reached, which does not belong to a component.
